text: Frida Erika Appelgren, earlier married Muranius,UNT.se 20 september 2008: Frida Muranius skiljer sig, accessdate: 19 July 2011 born 5 April 1981 in Malmö, Sweden, is a Swedish music artist. She scored a mid-2007 hit with the song Dunka mig gul och blå. Together with Headline she participated at Melodifestivalen 2008 with the song Upp o hoppa. The song ended up 10th in the finals. ==Discography== *Gasen I Botten (rap.
